title: Malcolm Holcombe - 3 Studio Albums + 3 Live Songs
description:
3 Albums from North Carolina growly-voiced singer and thrashy guitar picker Malcolm Holcombe:
A Hundred Lies
I Never Heard You Knockin'
Not Forgotten
+ 3 Live At A NYC benefit for a bar.

When I bought "A Hundred Lies" there was a sticker with a blurb from Lucinda Williams on it, so she is a fan, apparently.

If you like this artist, check out his music online, buy his CDs and support him in live settings. Tip generously.
